ud and Quiet]]|issue=62|accessdate=January 4, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221075652/http://www.loudandquiet.com/2014/10/the-innocents-by-weyes-blood/|archivedate=December 21, 2014}}</ref>\n| rev4 = ''[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]]''\n| rev4Score = 7.7/10<ref>{{cite web|last=Deusner|first=Stephen M.|date=October 28, 2014|url=http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/19792-weyes-blood-the-innocents/|title=Weyes Blood: The Innocents|work=[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]]|accessdate=January 4, 2015}}</ref>\n| rev5 = ''[[PopMatters]]''\n| rev5Score = 7/10<ref>{{cite web|last=James|first=Matt|date=October 29, 2014|url=http://www.popmatters.com/review/187079-weyes-blood-the-innocents/|title=Weyes Blood: The Innocents|work=[[PopMatters]]|accessdate=January 4, 2015}}</ref>\n| rev6 = ''[[Tiny Mix Tapes]]''\n| rev6Score = 4/5<ref>{{cite web|last=Roylance|first=Ben|url=http://www.tinymixtapes.com/music-review/weyes-blood-the-innocents|title=Weyes Blood \u2013 The Innocents|work=[[Tiny Mix Tapes]]|accessdate=January 4, 2015}}</ref>\n| rev7 = ''[[Uncut (magazine)|Uncut]]''\n| rev7Score = 8/10<ref>{{cite journal|title=Weyes Blood: The Innocents|work=[[Uncut (magazine)|Uncut]]|issue=210|date=November 2014|page=84}}</ref>\n}}\n\n'''''The Innocents''''' is the second studio album by American musician [[Weyes Blood]]. The album was released on October 21, 2014 by [[Mexican Summer]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://weyesblood.bandcamp.com/album/the-innocents|title=The Innocents|website=Weyes Blood|access-date=November 6, 2018}}</ref>\n\n== Track listing ==\n{{Track listing\n| all_writing = [[Weyes Blood|Natalie Mering]]\n| lyrics_credits = \n| music_credits = \n| extra_column = \n| title1 = Land of Broken Dreams\n| note1 = \n| length1 = 4:31\n| writer1 = \n| extra1 = \n| title2 = Hang On\n| note2 = \n| length2 = 3:45\n| writer2 = \n| extra2 = \n| title3 = Some Winters\n| note3 = \n| length3 = 6:15\n| writer3 = \n| extra3 = \n| title4 = Summer\n| note4 = \n| length4 = 2:47\